Dynamic optimization or optimal control is of major significance in fields of sciences, management, engineering and economics. Optimal control helps in identifying parameters which can control certain variables to produce the optimum result. In this section, we extend the system of equation (1) by adding 3 control parameters \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
