				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$u_{3}$$\end{document}u3 and develop the optimal control problem. The control \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
