				\begin{document}$$u_{3}$$\end{document}u3 is added to improve the quarantine and hospitalization rate of the identified infected population. This is necessary and will help in controlling the further spread of disease from this set of infectives, as the chances of them coming in contact with susceptible will be decreased majorly. \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
